grub_cmd: menuentry Debian GNU/Linux --class debian --class gnu-linux --class gnu --class os --id gnulinux-simple-d4b018ac-5304-4aac-b870-4060a39e2af1 {
	load_video
	insmod gzio
	if [ x$grub_platform = xxen ]; then insmod xzio; insmod lzopio; fi
	insmod part_gpt
	insmod ext2
	set root='hd0,gpt3'
	if [ x$feature_platform_search_hint = xy ]; then
	  search --no-floppy --fs-uuid --set=root --hint-bios=hd0,gpt3 --hint-efi=hd0,gpt3 --hint-baremetal=ahci0,gpt3  d4b018ac-5304-4aac-b870-4060a39e2af1
	else
	  search --no-floppy --fs-uuid --set=root d4b018ac-5304-4aac-b870-4060a39e2af1
	fi
	echo	'Loading Linux 5.10.0-rc1+ ...'
	linuxefi	/boot/vmlinuz-5.10.0-rc1+ root=UUID=d4b018ac-5304-4aac-b870-4060a39e2af1 ro  quiet
	echo	'Loading initial ramdisk ...'
	initrdefi	/boot/initrd.img-5.10.0-rc1+
}
